MusicalPianoApp 🎹
A WPF-based virtual piano application built using C# and XAML. Explore musical notes interactively and enjoy a beautifully styled interface.

Features ✨
🎵 Interactive piano keys with a custom-styled UI.
🌟 Smooth hover and press animations for keys.
🛠 Built using WPF for a modern desktop application feel.
📖 "About Piano" section to learn more about the application.
🚪 Exit functionality with a single click.


Installation 🚀
Clone the repository: https://github.com/mahasan24/WpfPianoApp/blob/main/piano.sln
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/MusicalPianoApp.git  
Open the project in Visual Studio.
Build the project to restore dependencies.
Run the application and start playing!

Technologies Used 🛠️
C#: Logic and event handling.
WPF (Windows Presentation Foundation): For UI design.
XAML: For declarative UI styling and layout.

How to Use 🎶
Launch the app to see the piano keys.
Click on the keys (A, B, C, D, E, F) to simulate piano sounds.
Use the "Exit" button to close the app.
Explore additional functionality through the "About Piano" section.
